[
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> then <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">This</st> is the <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">place</st> where the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> will be, <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">along with</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> for <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">ordered</st> the <st data-num=\"01616 0834\">resident foreigners</st><n id=\"1\" /> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> to be <st data-num=\"03664\" class=\"\">called together</st>. He <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">appointed</st> some of them to be <st data-num=\"02672\" class=\"\">stonecutters</st> to <st data-num=\"02672\" class=\"\">chisel</st> <st data-num=\"068 01496\">stones</st> for the <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">building</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">supplied</st> a <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">large amount</st> of <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> for the <st data-num=\"04548\" class=\"\">nails</st> of the <st data-num=\"01817\" class=\"\">doors</st> of the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gates</st> and for <st data-num=\"04226\" class=\"\">braces</st>, <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">more</st> <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st> <st data-num=\"0369\">than could be</st> <st data-num=\"04948\" class=\"\">weighed</st>, ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "and more <st data-num=\"0730\" class=\"\">cedar</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">logs</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">than could be</st> <st data-num=\"04557\" class=\"\">counted</st>. (The <st data-num=\"06722\" class=\"\">Sidonians</st> and <st data-num=\"06876\" class=\"\">Tyrians</st> had <st data-num=\"03588 0935\">brought</st> a <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">large amount</st> of <st data-num=\"0730\" class=\"\">cedar</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">logs</st> to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>.) </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cMy <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st> is just an <st data-num=\"07390\" class=\"\">inexperienced</st> <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> to be <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> must <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"04605\" class=\"\">especially</st> <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">magnificent</st> so it will become <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">famous</st> and be considered <st data-num=\"08597\" class=\"\">splendid</st> by <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">nations</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> Therefore I will <st data-num=\"03559 04994\">make preparations</st> for its construction.\u201d So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">made</st> <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">extensive</st> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">preparations</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> he <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">died</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">He <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st> and <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">charged</st> him to <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st>: \u201cMy <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> really <st data-num=\"01961 05973 03824\">wanted</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> to <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">honor</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> my <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "But this <st data-num=\"01961 0559\">was</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> me: \u2018You have <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">spilled</st> a <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">great deal</st> of <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">fought</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battles</st>. You must <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> to <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">honor</st> me,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> you have <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">spilled</st> a <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great deal</st> of <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> on the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> me.",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, you will <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">have</st> a <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">who</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> a <st data-num=\"04496\" class=\"\">peaceful</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">give</st> him <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">rest</st> from <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> on <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">every side</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st><n id=\"3\" /> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> his <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>; I will <st data-num=\"05414 05921\">give</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st> and <st data-num=\"08253\" class=\"\">quiet</st> during his <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">reign</st>.<n id=\"4\" />",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> will <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> to <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">honor</st> me;<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, and <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will become his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>. I will <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">grant</st> to his <st data-num=\"04438\" class=\"\">dynasty</st> <st data-num=\"05704 05769\">permanent</st> <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">rule</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\">Israel</st>.\u2019<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201c<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, may the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you! May you <st data-num=\"06743\" class=\"\">succeed</st> and <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, just <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> he <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">announced</st> you <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">would</st>.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">Only</st> may the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> you <st data-num=\"07922\" class=\"\">insight</st> and <st data-num=\"0998\" class=\"\">understanding</st> when he <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">places</st> you <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">in charge</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">of</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, so you may <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">obey</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">Then</st> you will <st data-num=\"06743\" class=\"\">succeed</st>, <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> you <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">carefully</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">obey</st> the <st data-num=\"02706\" class=\"\">rules</st> and <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">regulations</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">ordered</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> <st data-num=\"05921\">to give to</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02388 0553\">Be</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">strong</st> and <st data-num=\"0553\" class=\"\">brave</st>! <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st> and <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">panic</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "Now, <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">look</st>, I have made <st data-num=\"06040\" class=\"\">every effort</st> to <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">supply what is needed</st> to build the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I have stored up <st data-num=\"03967 0505\">100,000</st> <st data-num=\"03603\" class=\"\">talents</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, <st data-num=\"0505 0505\">1,000,000</st> <st data-num=\"03603\" class=\"\">talents</st><n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>, and <st data-num=\"03588 01961\">so</st> <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">much</st> <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st> and <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> it <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">cannot be</st> <st data-num=\"04948\" class=\"\">weighed</st>, <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">as well as</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wood</st> and <st data-num=\"068\" class=\"\">stones</st>. Feel free to <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">add</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">more</st>! ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "You also <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">have available</st> <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">many</st> <st data-num=\"06213 04399\">workers</st>, including <st data-num=\"02672\" class=\"\">stonecutters</st>, <st data-num=\"02796 068\">masons</st>, <st data-num=\"02796 06086\">carpenters</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and an <st data-num=\"0369 04557\">innumerable</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">array</st> of <st data-num=\"04399\" class=\"\">workers</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">who</st> are <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">skilled</st>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "in using <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>, <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st>, and <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Get up</st> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">begin the work</st>! May the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you!\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">ordered</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> to <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">support</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"08010\" class=\"\">Solomon</st>. ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "He told them,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you!<n id=\"2\" /> He has <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">made</st> you <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">secure</st> on <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">every side</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">handed</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">over</st> to me the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">region</st><n id=\"4\" /> and the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">region</st><n id=\"5\" /> is <st data-num=\"03533\" class=\"\">subdued</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">and</st> his <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>. ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"05414 03824\">wholeheartedly</st> and with your <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">entire being</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Get up</st> and <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> the <st data-num=\"04720\" class=\"\">sanctuary</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>! Then you can <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> and the <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">holy</st> <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">items</st> dedicated to <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> service<n id=\"3\" /> into the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> that is <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> to <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">honor</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  }
]